  "prompt": "Which is the best camera phone performance under 10000?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, several smartphones under the \u20b910,000 price point offer impressive camera performance. Here are a few models that are generally well-regarded for their camera capabilities in that budget:\n\n1. **Realme Narzo 30**: This phone features a capable 48 MP main camera and performs well in various lighting conditions. It also offers decent color reproduction and detail.\n\n2. **Xiaomi Redmi Note 10**: Known for its 48 MP quad-camera setup, the Redmi Note 10 delivers excellent photos for its price. It\u2019s especially good in well-lit environments.\n\n3. **Samsung Galaxy M12**: The Galaxy M12 sports a 48 MP camera and is known for its good color accuracy and decent low-light performance, plus Samsung's software optimizations enhance photo quality.\n\n4. **Poco M3 Pro**: This phone comes with a versatile camera setup, including a 48 MP main shooter, which can capture good quality images, especially in good lighting.\n\n5. **Motorola Moto G Power (2021)**: Although not exclusive to India, if you find it in your region, it has a solid camera performance, focusing on practicality and consistency.\n\nWhen considering a purchase, it's a good idea to look at recent user reviews, each phone's photo samples, and software updates that may improve camera performance. It's best to compare specific model features and read current reviews, as smartphone offerings frequently change and new models are released.",
